Body:
Description: Hello Team,

One of our clients has forgotten their credentials, and despite attempting to log in using the root account, we are still unable to gain access. We kindly request that you reset the password at your earliest convenience.
Steps to Reproduce Updated: Missing password

What We've Learned Updated: in sf_guard_user there is just one admin, and no root account.
Password was reset as soon as I received the approval from the devops team.
Next Steps Updated: Reset the password
